  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To describe the safety and tolerability of 80 weeks of subcutaneous (SC) evolocumab (AMG 145)
      when added to standard of care in pediatric subjects 10 to 17 years of age with HeFH or HoFH.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
